    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/be79343ee1ba7ef938389615ea817acc.avif?t=1771473683\" width=600 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">当然。这里是你的文案 <strong>中文（简体）版本</strong>，保持同样的结构与氛围，直接粘贴到 Steam 即可：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>种植。销售。扩张。守护你的家园。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>The Hawkers</strong> 融合了农场模拟的温馨感与商店经营的紧张刺激。你不只是收获作物……你是在 <strong>打造一种生活</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">播种、饲养动物、制作商品、设计并经营你的店铺，成为小镇经济的核心。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">但你的成功越大，一件令人不安的事就越清晰：<br><strong>有人正在悄无声息地买下这里的一切……</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌱 <strong>从土地到货架</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在日复一日的成长周期中种植、浇水并收获作物。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >饲养动物、管理资源，提升你的产出效率。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作并加工商品，以最佳价格出售。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升技能等级，解锁更多农场玩法与可能性。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/b6fd7b73b5bb841c8ccff5a3249d849f.poster.avif?t=1771473683\" width=600 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/b6fd7b73b5bb841c8ccff5a3249d849f.webm?t=1771473683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🏪 <strong>你的店铺，你说了算</strong><br>从零开始打造你的商店，让它真正属于你。</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由定制布局：货架、装饰与空间规划。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >决定出售哪些商品，以及如何陈列展示。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >管理利润、持续再投资，一步步扩张规模。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受悠闲日常……也要应对客流高峰与难以预测的顾客。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/343a88b3bc318ab0c441de464d3520d2.poster.avif?t=1771473683\" width=416 height=64 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/343a88b3bc318ab0c441de464d3520d2.webm?t=1771473683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/6cd08c599f0c3c048de7c5c9fb6b128c.avif?t=1771473683\" width=1155 height=978 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧠 <strong>不失“温馨感”的经营策略（Tycoon）</strong><br>你的每个决定都很关键：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >平衡时间、资金与生产节奏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >规划升级：农场、店铺、工具与家园。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >优化成长路线，建立一个可持续扩张的商业帝国。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧑‍🤝‍🧑 <strong>小镇、角色与关系</strong><br>结识居民、建立关系，在社区里找到你的位置。</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有个性、有日常作息、带小故事的 NPC。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >事件与特别时刻，让小镇充满生命力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的成长不只用金钱衡量——也包括人与人之间的联结。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/329de5b93ea7eae9e798f5c5eeeb3126.poster.avif?t=1771473683\" width=630 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/329de5b93ea7eae9e798f5c5eeeb3126.webm?t=1771473683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/f1d8ab74474305ca29235bb0b57083a5.poster.avif?t=1771473683\" width=126 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/f1d8ab74474305ca29235bb0b57083a5.webm?t=1771473683\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🕯️ <strong>平静之下的隐藏谜团</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">故事始于你童年与祖父的回忆……多年后你再次回到小镇。<br>一位强势的商人（<strong>Mr. Bunny</strong>）正在悄悄收购周围的一切。<br><strong>你的目标不只是成功——而是阻止小镇走向消失。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">🎨 <strong>有灵魂的像素画风</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">温暖的像素美术、柔和配色与用心打磨的细节，营造出怀旧而舒适的氛围……同时，背后又藏着一丝神秘阴影。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>现在加入愿望单，并关注开发进展。</strong><br><strong>The Hawkers</strong> 正在开发中；部分功能可能会随着时间调整与进化。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3105060/extras/77c91a6e8bfc0fa0fa63c6da973d3769.avif?t=1771473683\" width=252 height=198 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">✨ <strong>在 Kickstarter 上支持 The Hawkers！</strong> ✨</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在 Kickstarter 搜索：<strong>“The Hawkers ♥ Pixel Art Farm Sim - Harvest, Build &amp; Live”</strong> 🌾🐓🌱</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
